  <summary date="2019-06-28T04:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Deepfakes Report Act of 2019

This bill requires the Science and Technology Directorate in the Department of Homeland Security to report at specified intervals on the state of digital content forgery technology. Digital content forgery is the use of emerging technologies, including artificial intelligence and machine learning techniques, to fabricate or manipulate audio, visual, or text content with the intent to mislead.</summary>
